      "x": 1155, "y": 456,
      "width": 300, "height": 150,
      "text": "Python / Flask\nPort: 5010 ext → 5000 int\n\nScrapers: Steam · Epic · GOG · Xbox\n\nEndpoints:\nGET /api/v1/games/search?name=\nGET /api/v1/games/compare?name=\nGET /api/v1/games/trending/<store>\n\nPublishes: game_prices_queue (AMQP)\nBroker: RabbitMQProducer / PrintBroker",
