    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "legend_body",
      "x": 1505, "y": 162,
      "width": 335, "height": 440,
      "text": "1. LAYERED\nClient → Frontend → Gateway → Services\nClear tier separation; each tier only\ncalls the next layer down.\n\n2. CLIENT-SERVER\nBrowser (client) ↔ Next.js SSR (server)\nNext.js ↔ Gateway (HTTP REST)\nRequest-response over HTTP/HTTPS.\n\n3. API GATEWAY\nSingle entry point (:8080) for all\nclient-facing APIs. Routes, auth,\nrate limiting, idempotency centralized.\n\n4. PIPE & FILTER\nMiddleware pipeline inside Hono:\nRequest → CORS → requireAuth\n→ rateLimiter → idempotency → handler\nEach filter transforms/validates.\n\n5. PUBLISH-SUBSCRIBE\nScrapper publishes price updates to\ngame_prices_queue (AMQP / RabbitMQ).\nGateway subscribes & consumes.\nDecoupled async communication.\n\n6. EVENT-DRIVEN\nRabbitMQ msg → priceUpdateBus\n(Node.js EventEmitter) → SSE push\nto subscribed browser clients.\nReactive, loosely coupled.",
      "originalText": "1. LAYERED\nClient → Frontend → Gateway → Services\nClear tier separation; each tier only\ncalls the next layer down.\n\n2. CLIENT-SERVER\nBrowser (client) ↔ Next.js SSR (server)\nNext.js ↔ Gateway (HTTP REST)\nRequest-response over HTTP/HTTPS.\n\n3. API GATEWAY\nSingle entry point (:8080) for all\nclient-facing APIs. Routes, auth,\nrate limiting, idempotency centralized.\n\n4. PIPE & FILTER\nMiddleware pipeline inside Hono:\nRequest → CORS → requireAuth\n→ rateLimiter → idempotency → handler\nEach filter transforms/validates.\n\n5. PUBLISH-SUBSCRIBE\nScrapper publishes price updates to\ngame_prices_queue (AMQP / RabbitMQ).\nGateway subscribes & consumes.\nDecoupled async communication.\n\n6. EVENT-DRIVEN\nRabbitMQ msg → priceUpdateBus\n(Node.js EventEmitter) → SSE push\nto subscribed browser clients.\nReactive, loosely coupled.",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "strokeColor": "#374151",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
