    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "connectors_legend_body",
      "x": 1505, "y": 678,
      "width": 335, "height": 180,
      "text": "→ solid line   HTTP/REST (sync request-response)\n- - dashed     SSE / AMQP (async / streaming)\n↔ bidirectional  bidirectional connector\n\nPorts:\n:3000  frontend-service (ext)\n:8080  gateway-service (ext)\n:3001  user-service (ext) → :3000 int\n:5010  scrapper-service (ext) → :5000 int\n:5433  PostgreSQL (ext) → :5432 int\n:6379  Redis\n:5672  RabbitMQ AMQP\n:15672 RabbitMQ Management UI",
      "originalText": "→ solid line   HTTP/REST (sync request-response)\n- - dashed     SSE / AMQP (async / streaming)\n↔ bidirectional  bidirectional connector\n\nPorts:\n:3000  frontend-service (ext)\n:8080  gateway-service (ext)\n:3001  user-service (ext) → :3000 int\n:5010  scrapper-service (ext) → :5000 int\n:5433  PostgreSQL (ext) → :5432 int\n:6379  Redis\n:5672  RabbitMQ AMQP\n:15672 RabbitMQ Management UI",
